Text: AddressesHow are all of you doing Everythings going well with us Farrell and I went home for Thanksgiving It was our first time back home since the wedding It was kinda strange because since we live nearby each other we had to decide whos house we were going to stay at and when Oh the joys of being married and having to split your time between the families It was good to see his mom because we hadnt seen her since she started her chemo treatments Shes doing well shes pretty much lost all of her hair but she is now getting some of her strength back She goes back to Houston next week for her fourth treatment and theyll do a sonogram to see how the tumor is doing She will most likely have a mastectomy in the next few months and then well just go from there We also drove up to Austin last Thursday night for the game of Friday GO HORNS What a fun game that was I had been debating on whether or not I was going to go because I had surgery the Thursday before tonsillectomy YUK It was hard to not be able to scream after we scored touchdown after touchdown I saw a lot of our pledge sisters at the game Lindsay Erica Stacey etc I was kinda out of it though because I was on a lot of pain medication so they probably thought I was nuts Anyway I just wanted to make sure I have all of your correct addresses Corey and Susan do yall still live in the same places And Elizabeth I think youve moved so can you just email me your address again Thanks Yall write back and let me know whats been going on with all of you Love Steph The information transmitted is intended only for the person or entity to which it is addressed and may contain confidential andor privileged material Any review retransmission dissemination or other use of or taking of any action in reliance upon this information by persons or entities other than the intended recipient is prohibited If you received this in error please contact the sender and delete the material from any computer

HeyHey girls I cant believe I missed seeing yall this weekend Im so sadFarrell and I had to leave early the next morning cause he had work its football season I told yall he got a new job right He is the JV Defensive Coordinator at Highland Park He loves it I would love to get together with yall soon I will be in Austin this weekend and for all of the home games Are you going to Austin for the game this weekend Susan Lets try and make plans to do something I cant believe that Elizabeth is engaged I am so happy for her I called her yesterday and left a message Do yall know any details about the wedding etc Chas and Laura have set their date April We are all so excited Let me know what yalls plans are for this weekend Miss you Steph The information transmitted is intended only for the person or entity to which it is addressed and may contain confidential andor privileged material Any review retransmission dissemination or other use of or taking of any action in reliance upon this information by persons or entities other than the intended recipient is prohibited If you received this in error please contact the sender and delete the material from any computer
